1
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:16,790
(You Chen'an and
Madam Yulan has escaped,)

2
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:18,319
(leaving behind
a trail of dying Tang people)

3
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:20,229
(who were abused by their cruelty.)

4
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:22,910
(To think You Chen'an was planning)

5
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:24,470
(to poison the entire city of Jiaozhou.)

6
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,029
(He has no regard for human life.)

7
00:00:27,359 --> 00:00:28,869
(He's lost his humanity.)

8
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,509
(Thank goodness)

9
00:00:32,079 --> 00:00:34,470
(I'm familiar with this parasite.)

10
00:00:36,079 --> 00:00:37,790
(I shall work with His Highness)

11
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,390
(to save Jiaozhou)

12
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:42,189
(and everyone else)

13
00:00:42,399 --> 00:00:43,589
(from the deadly outbreak.)

14
00:00:56,360 --> 00:01:01,630
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

15
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:06,390
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

16
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:10,670
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

17
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:15,870
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

18
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:18,639
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

19
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:21,479
♪The surface always conceals♪

20
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:26,670
♪Separate cause and effect♪

21
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,399
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

22
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,039
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

23
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:36,879
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

24
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:41,910
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

25
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:47,470
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

26
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:52,950
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

27
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:58,230
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

28
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:00,590
♪Until it is set free♪

29
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:15,039
=The Imperial Coroner S2=
(Adapted from Idle Girl's The Constable's Wife)

30
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:18,119
(This story is entirely fictional.)

31
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,950
=Episode 26=

32
00:02:21,050 --> 00:02:22,110
We don't have enough herbs?

33
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,350
The herbs requested by Princess Consort
are mostly uncommon.

34
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,510
Moreover, Jiaozhou has been facing
a severe lack of herbs in recent years.

35
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:30,370
I've searched all over Jiaozhou,
but still can't get most of the herbs,

36
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,110
so I'm asking for your help.

37
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,469
Some of the patients

38
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,909
are in critical condition.

39
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,670
Those parasites might dig their way out
from their stomachs anytime.

40
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,469
If their condition is not treated,

41
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:41,270
I...

42
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:41,990
I'm afraid...

43
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:44,160
I wish we could conquer Nanzhao

44
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,710
and raid their herbs.

45
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:47,189
Nanzhao's herbs?

46
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,349
Perhaps there's someone who can help.

47
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,390
Summon the Maritime Trade Supervisor.

48
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,190
Yes, Your Highness.

49
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,589
Greetings, Your Highness.

50
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,749
I have an urgent matter

51
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,469
that requires your help.

52
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,270
You're too courteous, Your Highness.

53
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,990
Eunuch Jinbao has already
written us a letter.

54
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:11,230
We know you have
a heavy responsibility to shoulder.

55
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,789
Just tell us what you need.

56
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,510
I'm sure you've heard

57
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,399
that outside the city walls,

58
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,990
there's a group of hostages
rescued from Nanzhao's detention camp.

59
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,400
They need a large amount of herbs.

60
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,990
Can you retrieve some herbs

61
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,349
from the trading ships?

62
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,749
I will pay as required.

63
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,079
Your Highness,

64
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,999
I thank you for your consideration.

65
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,309
However, there's not much money left

66
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,189
in our treasury now.

67
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:38,189
I remember that trade taxes
form the largest component

68
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,909
of Jiaozhou's revenue in past years.

69
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:43,189
Things are different now.

70
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:45,390
Ever since conflicts
broke out in the south,

71
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,718
trading activities

72
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:48,309
have deteriorated.

73
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,749
We got plundered by the Nanzhao soldiers,

74
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,629
and borders were shut down without notice.

75
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,430
I will do my best

76
00:03:55,599 --> 00:03:57,029
to retrieve those herbs.

77
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,950
If you're willing to help,

78
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:01,349
I'm sure you will succeed.

79
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,749
If war truly breaks out,

80
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,309
the borders would be closed,

81
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,629
and everyone in Jiaozhou
would die of starvation.

82
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,830
By then, I would be irrelevant,

83
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,400
and I'd be on my way to the capital

84
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:14,869
to receive punishment.

85
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,109
Distribute this around.

86
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,830
Your Highness.

87
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,270
Everyone,

88
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,789
take a sip.

89
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,549
Here.

90
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,070
It's here.

91
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,229
Here's the medicine.

92
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,070
Give it to the children first.

93
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,190
Granny?

94
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,719
I'm fine.

95
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,799
Let the youngsters have it.

96
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:57,610
♪Fireflies like stars
circle through the seasons♪

97
00:04:57,700 --> 00:05:03,970
♪Shining with the hope of dreams,
this world is no longer in rags♪

98
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:08,659
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

99
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:11,930
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

100
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:12,559
Quick!

101
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:18,930
♪Together we face the tides of fate,
turning the course of heaven and earth♪

102
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:25,930
♪This love was never easy,
so life and death will not part us♪

103
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:33,939
♪Like sinking into the deep sea,
the first breath upon awakening♪

104
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:40,890
♪This bond will never waver, so we
stay together till our hair turns white♪

105
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:49,130
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen,
and write the ending of eternity♪

106
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,119
It's only been a few days.

107
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,190
You've lost much weight.

108
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,270
How impressive of you.

109
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,589
You managed to gather so many herbs
in these few days.

110
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,270
But...

111
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,909
What else is missing?

112
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,950
If you need anything,

113
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,750
I'll search for it.

114
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,070
We have enough herbs now,

115
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,789
but

116
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,349
they can only relieve pain.

117
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,669
It's not a long-term solution.

118
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:33,239
Recently, I've been working with doctors
and physicians from all over

119
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,349
to formulate an antidote,

120
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,349
but we still haven't found
an effective panacea.

121
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,669
We had to lie to those people.

122
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,789
You lied?

123
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,229
To lift their spirits

124
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:47,989
and give them the will to live,

125
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,310
I lied to them

126
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,630
that they'd recover as long as
they receive treatment.

127
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,909
But I'm not even sure about that.

128
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,549
It doesn't feel good to deceive them.

129
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:59,589
Whenever I see them,

130
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,150
I feel the guilt biting my conscience.

131
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,669
This pair of hands

132
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,710
has only held a coroner's scalpel,

133
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:10,789
not taking pulses
or performing acupuncture.

134
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:15,870
This isn't deception.

135
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,510
It's encouragement.

136
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,469
You gave them hope to live.

137
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,229
It was you

138
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:22,549
who risked your life

139
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,029
to find an antidote.

140
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,109
It was you

141
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:29,190
who stopped the parasites
from spreading,

142
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:32,390
protecting the citizens of Jiaozhou.

143
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,229
You're worthy of trust,

144
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,989
so believe in yourself.

145
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,229
(Jinyu.)

146
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,669
(The Nanzhao Army is assembling
in a massive scale.)

147
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,270
(They might launch
an attack at Jiaozhou's borders anytime.)

148
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,750
That note.

149
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,029
"Until the new king ascends,
the nation shall die."

150
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,989
It seems that Liu Shijiang
was just the beginning.

151
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,549
Nanzhao

152
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:19,549
is planning to sacrifice so many lives
to boost their morale.

153
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:22,429
(The King of Nanzhao and You Chen'an)

154
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,039
(Nanzhao)
(are certain that His Majesty)

155
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,270
(wouldn't sit by and watch.)

156
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:41,390
Chen Feng.

157
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:42,690
Yes, Your Highness.

158
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,309
Hand this to Zhou Han personally.

159
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,800
Make sure the contents don't leak.

160
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:46,590
Yes, Your Highness.

161
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:53,370
(Zhennan Pass)

162
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,429
Go!

163
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:57,590
Go!

164
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,029
Go!

165
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,630
You start this war
and retreat as you please.

166
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,470
You don't care
about my brother's safety.

167
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,150
He's done so much

168
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,110
for you and for Nanzhao,

169
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:16,309
yet he's being held hostage
by the Great Tang.

170
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,590
Who knows how he's being tortured?

171
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:19,990
What if...

172
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,470
Don't worry.

173
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,789
Your brother is
a valuable hostage to them.

174
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,549
They wouldn't kill him.

175
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,470
What do you mean?

176
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:33,709
Does my brother deserve such cruelty?

177
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:36,390
My father led his army

178
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,878
to repel the Tubo at the northwest.

179
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:40,660
He hasn't even healed
from his old injuries.

180
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:43,789
And now, my brother is trapped
in Chang'an, his fate unknown.

181
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,750
My whole family
risked their lives for Nanzhao.

182
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,709
Nothing has come out of it.

183
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,630
And yet, you're patronizing me.

184
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,789
Why do I have to suffer so?

185
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:56,549
I wish I could save your brother too.

186
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,309
Blame Xiao Jinli and You Chen'an.

187
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:01,429
They're too cunning for us.

188
00:10:01,430 --> 00:10:03,590
Right now, the only thing in my
father's mind is conquering Jiaozhou.

189
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,709
As for your brother,

190
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:07,110
we'll have to wait until
we defeat the Great Tang.

191
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:08,949
You mean

192
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,470
my brother has to die?

193
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:11,990
I...

194
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,398
I'm not...

195
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:13,870
I...

196
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:21,990
Your Highness.

197
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:28,470
Your Highness.

198
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,549
If launching a war is risky,

199
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:33,230
we can initiate a barter instead.

200
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,270
What do you mean?

201
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:38,949
Explain the details.

202
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,949
I received some news

203
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,309
that someone in Jiaozhou

204
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,150
is paying good money for herbs.

205
00:10:46,519 --> 00:10:48,999
I was planning to earn a fortune

206
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,270
from this opportunity,

207
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:53,558
but I did some research

208
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,319
and found out the person buying the herbs

209
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,789
was Commandery Princess Consort An.

210
00:10:57,110 --> 00:10:59,870
She's using the herbs to cure
those hostages from the detention camp.

211
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:02,470
Since they need herbs,

212
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:04,029
we can provide.

213
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:05,029
But

214
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:08,309
we'll ask for Lord Gao's
safe return in exchange.

215
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,839
That's a marvelous idea!

216
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,918
We can use some herbs

217
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:12,949
to save my brother's life.

218
00:11:13,039 --> 00:11:14,029
It's a guaranteed win.

219
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,549
But...

220
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,669
Would Jiaozhou agree to this deal?

221
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,510
We'll have to thank

222
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:23,079
Madam Yulan

223
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,990
for leaving that note.

224
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,398
I've lived in the Great Tang before.

225
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:29,878
Everyone there

226
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:30,630
is obsessed

227
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:33,630
with ethics and etiquette.

228
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,189
To gain the people's support,

229
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,709
they'd agree to this deal.

230
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,110
But my father...

231
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:42,350
Your Highness.

232
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,870
You have lost some good men,

233
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:45,878
and Second Prince

234
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,390
has lost his detention camp.

235
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,709
The current situation is not
favorable towards Nanzhao.

236
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,210
Launching a military attack
may not be a wise solution.

237
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,069
If we offer to trade with herbs instead,

238
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:55,829
perhaps

239
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,270
we can request even more
from the Great Tang.

240
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,470
Zhou Han made an excellent point.

241
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,669
Talk to your father now.

242
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,370
Tell him exactly what Zhou Han said.

243
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,398
Any later,

244
00:12:07,399 --> 00:12:09,479
and You Chen'an might steal your credit.

245
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,669
He'd better not.

246
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,870
I'll talk to Father now.

247
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,470
You came up with this idea yourself?

248
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:20,909
Yes.

249
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:22,309
This is my idea.

250
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,230
I think

251
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,949
that a forceful attack is too risky,

252
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,300
so we should resort to strategy.

253
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,350
My son.

254
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,029
You've finally grown wiser.

255
00:12:33,279 --> 00:12:35,029
You know about strategies.

256
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,510
Still,

257
00:12:38,919 --> 00:12:41,429
offering herbs in return
for just Gao Luoqian's life

258
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,870
may seem like a good deal,

259
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:43,829
but it's actually

260
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:45,150
too much of a hassle.

261
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:46,669
Father?

262
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,189
Since we're initiating a deal,

263
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,510
let's make it big.

264
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,949
Big?

265
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,270
Think about it.

266
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,029
We spent

267
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,390
so much effort

268
00:12:58,759 --> 00:13:01,359
to attack Jiaozhou and
throw Chang'an into disarray.

269
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,590
Why did we do so?

270
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,359
Naturally,

271
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,038
for land,

272
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:05,798
money

273
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,870
and resources.

274
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,829
Not just that.

275
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,350
Think again.

276
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:12,829
Jiaozhou is by the sea.

277
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:13,990
They have a huge port,

278
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,870
making it a key trade passage.

279
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:17,839
If we can take over this trade passage,

280
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:21,110
we can start trading freely
with everywhere.

281
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,758
Well said, Father.

282
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:25,518
Besides, the Great Tang
is too busy repelling enemies

283
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,789
from the north.

284
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:30,029
They have no military resources
to wage war in the south.

285
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:32,430
We can take advantage of this
and propose a peaceful negotiation,

286
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:35,069
signing a contract
that benefits Nanzhao.

287
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,500
If the deal goes through,
that would be great.

288
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:38,789
If not,

289
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,709
we can also use this chance

290
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,319
to assess the Great Tang's
true capabilities.

291
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,669
We still win in the end.

292
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,630
Wise words, Father.

293
00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:49,789
You'll be in charge of the negotiation.

294
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,549
Yes, Father.

295
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:52,470
Longsheng.

296
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,189
If it goes well,

297
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,750
you can take credit for this success.

298
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,909
That would be a load off my mind.

299
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,709
I can finally pass this kingdom

300
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,990
to your hands.

301
00:14:06,879 --> 00:14:08,470
All these years of nurturing you

302
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:11,069
would finally come to fruition.

303
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:13,990
I shall do my best.

304
00:14:18,559 --> 00:14:20,870
The king is biased towards Eldest Prince.

305
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:23,069
That's how it's always been, right?

306
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,150
He sees me as a stepping stone,

307
00:14:27,279 --> 00:14:28,669
a springboard

308
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,189
for my brother.

309
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:32,750
Once my brother ascends the throne,

310
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,750
I'd surely die.

311
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:36,789
The negotiation...

312
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:40,309
I must go.

313
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:43,390
But once we're at the negotiation,

314
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:46,630
things would be beyond our control.

315
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:51,949
Li Zhang.

316
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,909
Our fates are intertwined.

317
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,750
If I die,

318
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,949
you'd end up badly too.

319
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,150
Your Highness.

320
00:15:01,399 --> 00:15:02,029
I shall

321
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,669
dedicate my life towards you.

322
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:06,150
Keep a close eye on Jiaozhou.

323
00:15:07,159 --> 00:15:08,429
They haven't found an antidote,

324
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,829
so they're bound to take action.

325
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,150
If we can capture Chu Chu

326
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,549
or anyone

327
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,909
close to Xiao Jinyu,

328
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,789
we'd have more bargaining chips.

329
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:21,590
Yes, Your Highness.

330
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:27,130
(Prefect's Residence)

331
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,079
By the name of my king,

332
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,490
I have come to Jiaozhou to meet you.

333
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,239
My king and his eldest prince

334
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,990
pity the innocent subjects of Jiaozhou.

335
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,540
They do not want their lives
ravaged by war,

336
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:42,230
so we have come for peaceful talks.

337
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,429
Only when there's peace

338
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,189
can there be prosperity.

339
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,479
The Great Tang also hopes

340
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,800
that our subjects live in peace,

341
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:53,230
free from calamities.

342
00:15:53,519 --> 00:15:54,590
I shall write to His Majesty

343
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,270
about your intent.

344
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:02,630
Lord Han.

345
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:15,990
Everyone.

346
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:16,999
This negotiation

347
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,110
is of grave importance.

348
00:16:18,639 --> 00:16:19,909
We are open to such talks.

349
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,189
My Lord.

350
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,909
I think I ate something bad.

351
00:16:23,919 --> 00:16:25,150
I need to use the loo.

352
00:16:25,399 --> 00:16:26,270
Go.

353
00:16:29,879 --> 00:16:30,470
Everyone.

354
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:49,750
I have...

355
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,549
I have completed my task.

356
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,270
Get up.

357
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,678
It wasn't easy to get
the King of Nanzhao

358
00:16:57,679 --> 00:16:58,960
initiate a peaceful negotiation.

359
00:16:59,200 --> 00:16:59,909
Thank you.

360
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,638
Yes, Your Highness.

361
00:17:01,639 --> 00:17:03,959
It's all thanks to your
visionary strategy.

362
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,830
You planted me to spy on
that dumb prince, after all.

363
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:07,989
Your Highness,

364
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,310
can you also feel it?

365
00:17:09,519 --> 00:17:11,318
Only when I work for you

366
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:13,550
can I truly shine.

367
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,469
Has You Longsheng suspected anything?

368
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,630
No.

369
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,709
Everything went accordingly.

370
00:17:21,519 --> 00:17:23,390
When Feng delivered the letter,

371
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:26,150
the prince was arguing with his wife

372
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:28,469
over Gao Luoqian.

373
00:17:28,799 --> 00:17:30,469
So, I did as you said

374
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,949
and proposed a herb trade

375
00:17:32,039 --> 00:17:33,318
to persuade You Longsheng

376
00:17:33,319 --> 00:17:35,590
into coaxing the King of Nanzhao

377
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:37,390
so that they'd initiate
this negotiation.

378
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:38,709
That's wonderful.

379
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,509
A herb trade.

380
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:42,030
It's two birds with one stone.

381
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,070
Go.

382
00:17:59,759 --> 00:18:01,078
Rinse your clothes

383
00:18:01,079 --> 00:18:02,318
with hot water

384
00:18:02,319 --> 00:18:04,278
boiled with atractylodes and realgar

385
00:18:04,279 --> 00:18:05,550
to get rid of the foul smell.

386
00:18:05,599 --> 00:18:06,199
Understood?

387
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:06,990
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

388
00:18:07,359 --> 00:18:08,150
Take these.

389
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:09,949
Careful.

390
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,798
I should've brought those mugwort pills

391
00:18:22,799 --> 00:18:23,830
from the capital.

392
00:18:26,799 --> 00:18:28,469
Look what I brought.

393
00:18:30,079 --> 00:18:32,229
Leng Yue, what brings you here?

394
00:18:35,039 --> 00:18:35,429
Here.

395
00:18:35,599 --> 00:18:36,229
Come up.

396
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:37,679
On my way here,

397
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,199
I heard about the detention camp,

398
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:41,469
so I bought some food and herbs for you.

399
00:18:41,759 --> 00:18:43,550
This should help you temporarily.

400
00:18:44,359 --> 00:18:46,229
This is just what I need now.

401
00:18:46,839 --> 00:18:47,749
Bring them here.

402
00:18:47,759 --> 00:18:48,709
Bring everything up.

403
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,870
This room.

404
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:52,989
What do you call this?

405
00:18:53,079 --> 00:18:54,189
A telepathic connection.

406
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,669
Don't let the prince hear that.

407
00:18:56,839 --> 00:18:58,509
He might get jealous of me.

408
00:19:01,359 --> 00:19:02,269
Look at you.

409
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:05,150
Have you been exerting yourself?

410
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:08,030
Your cheeks have grown thinner.

411
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:10,350
I'm fine.

412
00:19:11,519 --> 00:19:13,509
Didn't Jing Yi come with you?

413
00:19:15,079 --> 00:19:16,749
He's no longer the little sparrow

414
00:19:17,119 --> 00:19:18,390
he once was.

415
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:22,670
I, Jing Yi, am Vice Minister of
the Court of Judicial Review.

416
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:25,030
I have been ordered
to audit the censorate

417
00:19:25,359 --> 00:19:27,229
and submit a report of
Jiaozhou's happenings.

418
00:19:28,039 --> 00:19:31,469
This sword represents
His Majesty's decree.

419
00:19:32,279 --> 00:19:34,269
- Hail the Emperor.
- Hail the Emperor.

420
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,390
You may rise.

421
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,838
It has been an exhausting trip,

422
00:19:39,839 --> 00:19:41,669
so we shall discuss work later.

423
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:43,909
Commandery Prince An may stay.

424
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,390
Are you the only one
in charge of this task?

425
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:56,038
Everyone else is journeying
at a snail's pace.

426
00:19:56,039 --> 00:19:57,870
Since I bear a royal decree,

427
00:19:58,319 --> 00:20:00,358
I had to travel day and night

428
00:20:00,359 --> 00:20:01,509
to...

429
00:20:07,359 --> 00:20:08,399
Yue and I

430
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:10,150
sneaked away from the main entourage.

431
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,469
As soon as Yue entered Jiaozhou,

432
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:12,838
she heard that Chu Chu
was treating the patients,

433
00:20:12,839 --> 00:20:13,830
so she went to visit her.

434
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,630
Your Highness, only I

435
00:20:15,759 --> 00:20:16,999
have been racking my brains...

436
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,310
What happened?

437
00:20:19,759 --> 00:20:21,070
You're still as stern as ever.

438
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,239
Back in the capital,

439
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,439
Huang Lv, Jiang Daohai

440
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:26,078
and other officials poisoned by Nanzhao

441
00:20:26,079 --> 00:20:27,870
have been imprisoned.

442
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:30,350
You could say I did something good.

443
00:20:30,599 --> 00:20:32,439
I thought I could take a break,

444
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,269
but

445
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,758
His Majesty was worried

446
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:36,229
of Jiaozhou's crisis.

447
00:20:36,599 --> 00:20:39,189
As a censor, there are many things
you can't decide,

448
00:20:39,519 --> 00:20:40,870
so I was ordered

449
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:43,509
to come and help you.

450
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:47,399
His Majesty has permitted you
to have the final say

451
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,110
on anything related to Nanzhao.

452
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,518
However, on my way here,

453
00:20:51,519 --> 00:20:53,630
I heard that Nanzhao
is preparing for peace talks.

454
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,469
You and His Majesty share the same mind.

455
00:21:00,839 --> 00:21:01,159
Cheng!

456
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,278
What should we do?

457
00:21:02,279 --> 00:21:03,590
Where's the physician?

458
00:21:04,799 --> 00:21:05,630
Where is he?

459
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,070
He's looking for herbs.

460
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,509
When will he be back?

461
00:21:09,759 --> 00:21:11,030
What should we do?

462
00:21:12,119 --> 00:21:12,989
The Princess is here.

463
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,038
Look at his leg!

464
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:15,358
What's wrong?

465
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,318
His leg!

466
00:21:16,319 --> 00:21:17,229
What happened?

467
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:19,709
Is it serious?

468
00:21:20,279 --> 00:21:21,110
Don't worry.

469
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:22,290
It's not the deadly parasite,

470
00:21:22,319 --> 00:21:23,269
just a tick.

471
00:21:24,359 --> 00:21:25,429
(Tick: A parasitic arachnid)
That's good.

472
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,550
(that feeds on animal blood)
What a relief.

473
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,790
However,

474
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:29,429
ticks are bloodsucking creatures.

475
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,110
We need to remove it.

476
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,269
Would it hurt?

477
00:21:33,279 --> 00:21:33,830
Good boy.

478
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:34,509
Don't be afraid.

479
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:35,870
I know how to make it not hurt.

480
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,830
What is that?

481
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:54,390
Don't be afraid.

482
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:07,269
It doesn't hurt anymore, right?

483
00:22:07,319 --> 00:22:09,070
I didn't feel a thing.

484
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,630
Sister, what's that?

485
00:22:12,119 --> 00:22:13,429
It's a painkiller.

486
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:15,030
When I was traveling,

487
00:22:15,279 --> 00:22:16,989
this was perfect

488
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,229
for small wounds.

489
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,749
Painkiller?

490
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,590
I think I've figured out a solution.

491
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,838
Removing the parasites by surgery?

492
00:22:27,839 --> 00:22:28,509
That's right.

493
00:22:29,079 --> 00:22:31,150
We did an autopsy on Liu Shijiang,

494
00:22:31,359 --> 00:22:33,429
(Autopsy)
and has been observing the patients.

495
00:22:33,759 --> 00:22:34,989
(Observing patients)
I can basically confirm

496
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:36,709
that once ingested, the parasites

497
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,830
live in the stomach's flesh.

498
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:41,790
(Use anesthesia)
We can anesthetize the patients,

499
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,630
remove the parasites quickly

500
00:22:43,799 --> 00:22:45,189
(Remove parasites)
and sew their wounds up

501
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:46,949
to save them.

502
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,989
But just now,

503
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,200
I operated on the child because
the tick was outside.

504
00:22:51,319 --> 00:22:53,469
Opening his stomach up
would be dangerous.

505
00:22:53,470 --> 00:22:55,550
It requires total knowledge
of the internal organs.

506
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:58,509
No doctor or physician

507
00:22:58,599 --> 00:23:00,358
has mastered such knowledge.

508
00:23:00,359 --> 00:23:01,030
I have.

509
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,159
No one here understands

510
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,310
internal organs better than I do.

511
00:23:05,599 --> 00:23:06,310
Besides,

512
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,719
I have extracted a poisonous pill

513
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,509
from Xu Rugui's body before,

514
00:23:11,279 --> 00:23:12,150
though it was

515
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,989
out of desperation.

516
00:23:14,279 --> 00:23:15,749
It's not a perfect solution,

517
00:23:16,319 --> 00:23:18,350
so we've never done this before.

518
00:23:19,119 --> 00:23:20,390
But given our current state,

519
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,909
to save these innocent people,

520
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,469
we have no choice.

521
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:25,989
We need to take the risk.

522
00:23:31,279 --> 00:23:32,150
Don't worry.

523
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,110
We have You Chen'an's help.

524
00:23:35,319 --> 00:23:36,150
The chart?

525
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:41,469
You Chen'an has killed
so many innocent people

526
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:42,989
to create the chart.

527
00:23:43,519 --> 00:23:44,790
So, I'm going to use it

528
00:23:45,519 --> 00:23:46,989
to save these innocent people.

529
00:23:49,090 --> 00:23:50,758
Hei and the others can't afford to wait.

530
00:23:50,759 --> 00:23:51,830
I need to take this risk.

531
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,870
Let's do it, then.

532
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:57,350
Instead of waiting to die,

533
00:23:57,839 --> 00:23:59,469
we should fight for survival.

534
00:23:59,599 --> 00:24:00,390
Sure.

535
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,749
Chu Chu, I'm with you.

536
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:02,669
Leng Yue.

537
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,318
What are the herbs used

538
00:24:04,319 --> 00:24:05,429
in that salve?

539
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,879
Thornapple,

540
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,630
peppermint,

541
00:24:07,839 --> 00:24:09,110
toad, wild ginger,

542
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:12,350
aconites and pepper.

543
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:15,469
These are common herbs.

544
00:24:15,799 --> 00:24:17,469
I'll get someone to buy them at Linzhou.

545
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:18,269
Great.

546
00:24:18,799 --> 00:24:21,110
Your Highness, buy as many as you can.

547
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,390
We'll operate

548
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,989
on the most critical patients first.

549
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:26,100
Jing Yi and I are preparing
for the negotiation.

550
00:24:26,119 --> 00:24:27,870
We'll be getting more herbs from them.

551
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,590
I'll send them over
as soon as we get them.

552
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,070
I understand your concern,

553
00:24:35,359 --> 00:24:36,239
but we don't know

554
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,870
how long this parasite

555
00:24:38,079 --> 00:24:39,070
will live in the body.

556
00:24:39,319 --> 00:24:40,590
They're highly poisonous.

557
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,509
If they release poison when they die,

558
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,469
it can be deadly.

559
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:47,269
More importantly,

560
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:49,350
as long as we don't
extract the parasites,

561
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:50,439
your lives

562
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,509
and Jiaozhou's safety

563
00:24:51,839 --> 00:24:53,390
will be at Nanzhao's whim.

564
00:24:58,079 --> 00:25:00,269
Your Highness, you can operate on me.

565
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:02,909
I'm old,

566
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,390
and I've lived enough.

567
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,159
If I can help you find a way

568
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:07,749
to save more lives,

569
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,070
at least I get to collect

570
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,509
some merit for my next life.

571
00:25:15,839 --> 00:25:17,429
Thank you, Granny Chunxi.

572
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,870
But

573
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,550
you're old,

574
00:25:20,759 --> 00:25:22,030
making the operation riskier

575
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:23,870
compared to those younger.

576
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,399
Also, this is my first operation,

577
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,709
so it'll take a long time.

578
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,830
Perhaps

579
00:25:29,759 --> 00:25:30,999
you're not the best choice.

580
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:32,030
Then...

581
00:25:33,279 --> 00:25:33,949
I'll go.

582
00:25:39,559 --> 00:25:41,189
Guo, stop that.

583
00:25:41,359 --> 00:25:42,159
How could we

584
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:44,070
risk a young girl's life?

585
00:25:44,359 --> 00:25:44,909
Your Highness.

586
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,030
Let me do it.

587
00:25:46,079 --> 00:25:46,989
I'm strong.

588
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:49,229
What's wrong with being a girl?

589
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:56,669
Your Highness and Miss Leng
are ladies too.

590
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:58,639
They must be more familiar

591
00:25:58,640 --> 00:25:59,590
with the female body.

592
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:02,630
I haven't taken many parasites,
and I'm young,

593
00:26:02,759 --> 00:26:03,709
so I'm the best choice.

594
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:08,989
Thank you, Guo.

595
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:24,299
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

596
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:28,090
♪Fireflies like stars
circle through the seasons♪

597
00:26:28,340 --> 00:26:34,890
♪Shining with the hope of dreams,
this world is no longer in rags♪

598
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:39,290
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

599
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,550
Guo?

600
00:26:43,119 --> 00:26:44,350
Your Highness.

601
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:48,030
Why aren't you sleeping?

602
00:26:48,359 --> 00:26:49,350
Come here.

603
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:56,610
♪This love was never easy,
so life and death will not part us♪

604
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:02,070
Are you feeling unwell?

605
00:27:02,799 --> 00:27:04,189
Your Highness,

606
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,870
I'm feeling a little scared.

607
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,550
Me too, actually.

608
00:27:11,599 --> 00:27:12,350
Guo.

609
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:14,390
When you stood up,

610
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:15,639
do you know how much

611
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,269
courage and confidence you gave me?

612
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,669
Right now, my only hope

613
00:27:19,039 --> 00:27:20,269
is to succeed.

614
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:22,909
Yeah.

615
00:27:23,279 --> 00:27:24,429
I believe in you.

616
00:27:26,519 --> 00:27:27,469
Thank you.

617
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,509
Guo.

618
00:27:28,559 --> 00:27:30,669
Can I call you Sister Princess?

619
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,669
Of course.

620
00:27:33,599 --> 00:27:34,669
Sister Princess.

621
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:37,550
You're nothing like the royals

622
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,909
I heard of.

623
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,278
How so?

624
00:27:41,279 --> 00:27:43,989
The royals are bullies,

625
00:27:44,279 --> 00:27:46,790
but you're so easy to approach,

626
00:27:47,079 --> 00:27:49,229
and you're willing to save us.

627
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:51,590
How are you a royal?

628
00:27:54,599 --> 00:27:55,590
Put it this way.

629
00:27:56,279 --> 00:27:58,509
Being a royal is just an identity.

630
00:27:58,720 --> 00:27:59,949
It's like

631
00:28:01,079 --> 00:28:02,189
a big family.

632
00:28:02,839 --> 00:28:04,669
There are all sorts of people

633
00:28:05,119 --> 00:28:07,509
with different personalities.

634
00:28:08,839 --> 00:28:09,749
Whether

635
00:28:09,839 --> 00:28:11,798
you do good or bad,

636
00:28:11,799 --> 00:28:13,350
it has nothing to do with identity,

637
00:28:13,759 --> 00:28:15,269
but your personality.

638
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,709
What a beautiful night.

639
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:24,350
So many stars.

640
00:28:24,759 --> 00:28:25,989
Sister Princess,

641
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:29,509
are the stars in Chang'an
the same as here?

642
00:28:32,279 --> 00:28:33,630
In Chang'an...

643
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,949
The night in Chang'an

644
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,550
is filled with lights

645
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,429
that can illuminate the sky.

646
00:28:40,119 --> 00:28:42,509
Illuminate the sky?

647
00:28:42,759 --> 00:28:44,669
How brilliant it must be.

648
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,669
When you recover,

649
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,790
I'll take you to Chang'an

650
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:51,429
to see the stars.

651
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:52,830
Sure.

652
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:12,490
(Tang)

653
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:06,439
I didn't see Second Prince's name

654
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:08,669
on the list of today's diplomats.

655
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,399
To think Second Prince

656
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:12,749
has resurrected from the dead.

657
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:14,959
My brother

658
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:15,630
is too eager

659
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:16,989
to claim credit.

660
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,439
Who knows what he did

661
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,100
to coax our father
into letting you come.

662
00:30:22,079 --> 00:30:24,429
Sorry for the embarrassment.

663
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,479
Father is worried
that you'd mess up again

664
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,749
if you come alone,

665
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,150
so I have been ordered

666
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:30,830
to keep an eye on you.

667
00:30:34,759 --> 00:30:36,669
Both of us have similar goals today.

668
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:37,830
Let's put away

669
00:30:38,279 --> 00:30:39,550
our past differences.

670
00:30:40,119 --> 00:30:41,469
I only hope we can work together

671
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,800
to make this negotiation a success

672
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,749
so that both kingdoms enjoy peace.

673
00:30:45,079 --> 00:30:46,429
Well said, Commandery Prince An.

674
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,830
So,

675
00:30:48,079 --> 00:30:49,390
let us begin.

676
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,110
Everyone.

677
00:30:50,559 --> 00:30:51,310
This way.

678
00:31:01,599 --> 00:31:02,189
Your Highness.

679
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,239
Guo has taken the medicine

680
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,110
and fallen asleep.

681
00:31:05,079 --> 00:31:05,669
Very well.

682
00:31:25,359 --> 00:31:27,749
Once we open up her stomach,
I will extract the parasites

683
00:31:27,839 --> 00:31:28,719
and stitch her up.

684
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,439
During this process,
we need to stop her bleeding

685
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,930
and keep a close eye on her condition.

686
00:31:32,599 --> 00:31:33,229
Leng Yue.

687
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,830
Work with the physicians
and brew the required medicine.

688
00:31:44,359 --> 00:31:45,390
Let's begin.

689
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:46,630
Yes, Your Highness.

690
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:56,350
This is the file on
Gao Luoqian's verdict.

691
00:32:03,799 --> 00:32:04,749
Commandery Prince An.

692
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:07,509
We've brought the herbs you listed down.

693
00:32:09,119 --> 00:32:09,790
List.

694
00:32:13,799 --> 00:32:15,110
Tally the herbs

695
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:16,989
and deliver to Jiaozhou immediately.

696
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:17,760
Yes, Your Highness.

697
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:20,798
Gao Luoqian is on the way back,
escorted by our soldiers.

698
00:32:20,799 --> 00:32:23,278
He will be handed
to the Nanzhao troops.

699
00:32:23,279 --> 00:32:24,310
Great.

700
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:52,310
"Setting up a Nanzhao Settlement
in Jiaozhou,

701
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:55,509
posting a market supervisor,
establishing a Nanzhao center..."

702
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,949
"Collecting 50% of the tax revenue"?

703
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:01,990
Commandery Prince An,

704
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,550
50%

705
00:33:04,119 --> 00:33:05,030
is too high.

706
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:07,469
These are the same terms
laid out to other kingdoms.

707
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,749
It's in black and white.

708
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:11,038
Well, then...

709
00:33:11,039 --> 00:33:11,949
Commandery Prince An.

710
00:33:14,839 --> 00:33:15,909
You and I both know

711
00:33:16,119 --> 00:33:17,439
that Nanzhao and the Great Tang

712
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,870
have an unusual relationship.

713
00:33:19,039 --> 00:33:20,790
Surely you can't apply
the same terms on us?

714
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,550
Commandery Prince An, I think

715
00:33:22,799 --> 00:33:23,949
you lack sincerity.

716
00:33:26,799 --> 00:33:28,830
The conditions Nanzhao is requesting

717
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:31,110
lack sincerity too.

718
00:33:33,599 --> 00:33:36,709
"The Great Tang shall hand over
half of Jiaozhou's trade rights

719
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:38,390
to be shared with Nanzhao".

720
00:33:38,759 --> 00:33:39,709
Eldest Prince,

721
00:33:40,839 --> 00:33:42,150
that's too much.

722
00:33:42,559 --> 00:33:43,630
Is it?

723
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,310
Commandery Prince An.

724
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:48,150
We've delivered those herbs to Jiaozhou,

725
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:49,880
even when Lord Gao
is still in your hands.

726
00:33:50,119 --> 00:33:51,959
We have nothing but good intents,

727
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,830
but you keep patronizing us.

728
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,669
Commandery Prince An,

729
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,269
do you really want

730
00:33:58,079 --> 00:33:59,469
to negotiate?

731
00:34:05,119 --> 00:34:06,590
Don't tell me Second Prince

732
00:34:06,599 --> 00:34:08,829
is actually the true mastermind
of this negotiation?

733
00:34:10,519 --> 00:34:12,110
Pardon my manners.

734
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:16,359
Or do you believe that Eldest Prince

735
00:34:16,360 --> 00:34:18,170
is unable to understand
the trade conditions?

736
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:20,590
You think he can't even tell

737
00:34:20,599 --> 00:34:21,789
whether I'm deceiving him?

738
00:34:22,519 --> 00:34:24,510
Who said I can't tell?

739
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:26,389
Longsheng,

740
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,630
they're sowing discord, don't fall for it.

741
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,829
Shut up.

742
00:34:33,039 --> 00:34:33,869
Yes.

743
00:34:34,079 --> 00:34:35,030
Commandery Prince An.

744
00:34:35,050 --> 00:34:37,070
Don't assume I don't understand
these conditions.

745
00:34:37,239 --> 00:34:39,389
It's inappropriate for the Great Tang

746
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,518
to pull these cheap tricks.

747
00:34:40,519 --> 00:34:41,558
We're negotiating now, aren't we?

748
00:34:41,559 --> 00:34:43,389
- Outrageous!
- How dare you!

749
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,269
We can negotiate about the rest,

750
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:21,829
but we insist on abolishing taxes
in the herb trade

751
00:35:22,519 --> 00:35:23,829
between Jiaozhou and Nanzhao.

752
00:35:27,239 --> 00:35:27,910
Very well.

753
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:30,510
We'll accept this to make amends
for our rudeness.

754
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:33,150
That sounds more like it.

755
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,150
Longsheng,

756
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:37,030
if we abolish herb taxes,

757
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:39,950
the herb traders in Nanzhao
will all head towards the Great Tang.

758
00:35:40,159 --> 00:35:41,829
This is working in their favor.

759
00:35:42,679 --> 00:35:43,669
Second Prince.

760
00:35:44,679 --> 00:35:46,759
When I insisted on collecting taxes,

761
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:48,630
you said it was deceit.

762
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:51,510
Now that I've agreed
to Eldest Prince's terms

763
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,950
and abolish taxes,

764
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,229
you still think it's deceit.

765
00:35:55,719 --> 00:35:57,510
So, whatever we do

766
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:00,550
will never satisfy you.

767
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:04,550
I...

768
00:36:05,239 --> 00:36:07,189
My pride is at stake here.

769
00:36:07,519 --> 00:36:08,749
What do you know?

770
00:36:21,639 --> 00:36:22,518
Jiaozhou agrees

771
00:36:22,519 --> 00:36:23,430
to exchange hostages.

772
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:25,349
Longsheng, they lack sincerity.

773
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:28,070
But Nanzhao must also
retreat their troops.

774
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,229
No, Longsheng.

775
00:36:31,119 --> 00:36:32,229
Give it some thought.

776
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,309
Careful, it's a trap.

777
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:36,700
Officers of Nanzhao, follow me,
we'll discuss the details at the back.

778
00:36:36,719 --> 00:36:37,349
Wait.

779
00:36:39,039 --> 00:36:39,829
Second Prince.

780
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,990
You keep interrupting the negotiation.

781
00:36:42,719 --> 00:36:44,110
What is your motive?

782
00:36:45,519 --> 00:36:47,399
Is Nanzhao really intent

783
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,749
on negotiating?

784
00:36:50,559 --> 00:36:52,510
Commandery Prince An, that's not it.

785
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:55,510
My father and I are serious
about this negotiation.

786
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,269
Be it the herb tax

787
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,789
or military retreat,

788
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:03,030
we have shown much tolerance.

789
00:37:03,639 --> 00:37:05,990
Eldest Prince,
I'm sure you can tell that.

790
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:09,349
We admire your sincerity,

791
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,678
but Second Prince...

792
00:37:12,679 --> 00:37:13,950
Second Prince,

793
00:37:14,519 --> 00:37:16,118
are you trying to negotiate

794
00:37:16,119 --> 00:37:17,709
or mess up?

795
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,919
Are you trying to mess us up,

796
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:21,439
or mess with Eldest Prince...

797
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,189
Jing Yi.

798
00:37:23,119 --> 00:37:24,070
That's enough.

799
00:37:25,519 --> 00:37:27,829
I'm sure Second Prince

800
00:37:28,159 --> 00:37:30,030
only wishes to advise Eldest Prince.

801
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,950
I know what I'm doing.

802
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,990
Stop being nosy.

803
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:13,990
Henceforth,

804
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,749
Nanzhao and the Great Tang

805
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,189
shall work hand in hand,

806
00:38:17,519 --> 00:38:18,789
and remain good neighbors.

807
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,389
The specifics

808
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,749
will have to be worked out,

809
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,389
but Eldest Prince's actions

810
00:38:24,519 --> 00:38:25,709
shall bring tremendous peace

811
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,150
to our kingdoms.

812
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:29,669
Well said, Commandery Prince An.

813
00:38:32,599 --> 00:38:33,470
Chen'an,

814
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:35,309
learn from us.

815
00:38:36,199 --> 00:38:37,910
What you see today,

816
00:38:38,599 --> 00:38:41,349
you may not see it again elsewhere.

817
00:38:43,639 --> 00:38:44,669
You're right, Longsheng.

818
00:38:48,079 --> 00:38:49,638
Today, we shall celebrate this

819
00:38:49,639 --> 00:38:51,269
with a drink.

820
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,389
Men!

821
00:38:53,239 --> 00:38:53,950
Serve the food!

822
00:39:06,239 --> 00:39:06,950
Your Highness.

823
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,590
Guo is safe now.

824
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:28,718
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

825
00:39:28,719 --> 00:39:29,389
Wait for me.

826
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:39,439
- She's here!
- How is she?

827
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,590
The operation was a success.

828
00:39:42,679 --> 00:39:45,999
Great, we're saved!

829
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,390
- It's a success!
- It's a success!

830
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:48,890
- It's a success!
- It's a success!

831
00:39:49,039 --> 00:39:50,630
- It's a success!
- It's a success!

832
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:52,630
We're saved!

833
00:39:54,559 --> 00:39:55,189
Come on.

834
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,910
Here's to our

835
00:39:57,119 --> 00:39:58,229
successful negotiation.

836
00:39:59,039 --> 00:39:59,709
Cheers.

837
00:40:07,079 --> 00:40:07,829
Your Highness.

838
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:10,070
The operation was a success.

839
00:40:12,239 --> 00:40:12,869
Go.

840
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,518
Here, Eldest Prince.

841
00:40:14,519 --> 00:40:15,110
Cheers.

842
00:40:19,639 --> 00:40:20,389
Second Prince.

843
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:31,430
Watch out, Longsheng!

844
00:41:02,340 --> 00:41:05,380
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

845
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:08,900
♪The hardships of arrival pass
in a fleeting blink♪

846
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:12,020
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

847
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:15,980
♪Leading us out of every winding turn♪

848
00:41:16,820 --> 00:41:20,620
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

849
00:41:20,620 --> 00:41:23,900
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

850
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:26,540
♪Your branches entwined with mine♪

851
00:41:26,540 --> 00:41:29,940
♪Bound together in mutual reliance♪

852
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:35,140
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

853
00:41:35,140 --> 00:41:38,220
♪Fireflies like stars circle
through the seasons♪

854
00:41:39,060 --> 00:41:41,180
♪Shining with the hope of dreams♪

855
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:45,860
♪This world is no longer in rags♪

856
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:50,220
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

857
00:41:50,220 --> 00:41:53,500
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

858
00:41:53,900 --> 00:41:56,220
♪Together we face the tides of fate♪

859
00:41:56,220 --> 00:42:00,380
♪Turning the course of heaven and earth♪

860
00:42:00,500 --> 00:42:03,100
♪This love was never easy♪

861
00:42:03,100 --> 00:42:07,500
♪So life and death will not part us♪

862
00:42:07,860 --> 00:42:10,420
♪Like sinking into the deep sea♪

863
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:15,420
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

864
00:42:15,420 --> 00:42:17,660
♪This bond will never waver♪

865
00:42:17,660 --> 00:42:22,540
♪So we stay together
till our hair turns white♪

866
00:42:22,540 --> 00:42:25,020
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen♪

867
00:42:25,020 --> 00:42:30,060
♪And write the ending of eternity♪

868
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:32,380
♪This love was never easy♪

869
00:42:32,380 --> 00:42:36,540
♪So I believe without doubt♪

870
00:42:37,180 --> 00:42:39,780
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

871
00:42:39,780 --> 00:42:44,700
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

872
00:42:45,180 --> 00:42:47,060
♪This bond will never waver♪

873
00:42:47,060 --> 00:42:52,060
♪So joy and sorrow
are no longer ours to choose♪

874
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:54,460
♪I will prove it
with the rest of my life♪

875
00:42:54,460 --> 00:43:00,220
♪Together at the edge
of the world without an end♪
